these singers that you're talking

00:56:43.300 --> 00:56:45.570
about are relatives of yours.

00:56:45.570 --> 00:56:46.870
&gt;&gt; Sheila Kay Adams: Yes.

00:56:46.870 --> 00:56:48.170
