And they'll spend -- Sam spent a
whole summer at my house, you know.

00:57:42.410 --> 00:57:44.480
And it's just wonderful.

00:57:44.480 --> 00:57:46.670
Branson was there for two years.

00:57:46.670 --> 00:57:47.970
&gt;&gt; Stephen Winnick: Yeah.

00:57:47.970 --> 00:57:51.340
&gt;&gt; Sheila Kay Adams: Yeah, so
that's what it's all about.

