by his parents.

01:00:16.490 --> 01:00:18.520
And isn't that amazing?

01:00:18.520 --> 01:00:19.820
&gt;&gt; Stephen Winnick: Yeah.

01:00:19.820 --> 01:00:21.120
&gt;&gt; Sheila Kay Adams: It looped
around the world, you know.

01:00:21.120 --> 01:00:28.000
Because that song that she sang
was the song that they sang

01:00:28.000 --> 01:00:33.250
