went around and checked the gates

01:00:33.250 --> 01:00:35.310
for all these little
pounds in Scotland.

01:00:35.310 --> 01:00:36.610
&gt;&gt; Stephen Winnick: Okay.

01:00:36.610 --> 01:00:38.900
&gt;&gt; Sheila Kay Adams: That
was the one that he sang

01:00:38.900 --> 01:00:41.620
