01:01:01.160 --> 01:01:02.460
&gt;&gt; Stephen Winnick: Very nice.

01:01:02.460 --> 01:01:03.760
&gt;&gt; Sheila Kay Adams: Nice.

01:01:03.760 --> 01:01:05.060
&gt;&gt; Stephen Winnick: So Her
Bright Smile Haunts Me Still.

01:01:05.060 --> 01:01:06.360
&gt;&gt; Sheila Kay Adams: Yep.

