Bright Smile Haunts Me Still.

01:01:10.000 --> 01:01:11.300
Yeah.

01:01:11.300 --> 01:01:12.600
&gt;&gt; Stephen Winnick: Right.

01:01:12.600 --> 01:01:14.380
So I mean, that experience
is sort of one

01:01:14.380 --> 01:01:19.330
of the universal experiences I
think that people who perform

01:01:19.330 --> 01:01:22.860
